--------------Road Map---------------------
Create Profile
    Name (String)
    Sex (ENUM)
    Age (int)
    Height (feet / meters) (Int)
    Height (inches / cm) (Int)
    Starting weight (lb/kg) (double)
    Starting Body Fat % (double)
    Imperial / Metric (ENUM)
    
Create Workout
    Add exercises to a workout
    Specify workout target (muscle groups, push, pull)
    specify available equipment
    files down available exercises

Create a plan
    Specify goals
    Add created workouts
    points out gaps in affected muscle groups

Track workout progress
    can pick a workout
    loads sets, reps, weight for each exercise
    can edit sets, reps, weight
    tracks intensity
    tracks rest time?
    auto saves
    uses current date

Track Body Progress
    See Chart with:
        weight
        body fat %
        calculated lean mass
        calculated fat mass
    Progress Pics

-------------NICE TO HAVE-------------

Create a custom exercise
    Name (String)
    muscle group (ENUM)
    push / pull (ENUM)

Trainer Account
    Link to clients
    monitor / edit plan

Calculate Calories / macros
